        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "title": "Backend DB Connection Pool (HikariCP)",
      "description": "Active and pending DB connections. If active connections hit the pool ceiling (10), DB writes queue up \u2014 this is the single-writer bottleneck made visible.",
